{"tid":908301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首辦外牆遭噴殘體「鄭月娥包庇兇犯」大字","createTime":"2018-11-19T13:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T04:13:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb33af09bd3fbd23c41362a8f2e6710a9282bd1","tid":908301,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181119/s00001/ae9a26a3eb5288002b7717be1d060d42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181119%2Fs00001%2Fae9a26a3eb5288002b7717be1d060d42.jpg&h=6c71d81c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官辦公室外牆遭人噴大字。警方下午12時25分接報，指一名男子在中環添華道特首辦圍牆，以白色噴漆噴上「郑月娥包庇凶犯　葵涌医院伤天害理」字句。涉事歹徒以涉嫌「刑事毀壞」當場被捕，事後被帶返警署調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場職員先在噴字範圍貼上黑膠布遮蓋，並以鐵欄圍封。至下午3時許，工人到場將大字妥善清理。"},{"pid":"1f798257f7815f31dcc4687e23a04f38e0c54d7c","tid":908301,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d21ba4f9b2f9596f5b48859233f9c910fc8e225","tid":908301,"uid":74778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"拉唔拉好<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181928ccdf2f02159622647d229e30baf05e79a3","tid":908301,"uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc831c77127e9d3abd0b5b9131498d0b89144fa1","tid":908301,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"講緊邊單呀"},{"pid":"e002f67f4c18f5502a309cf795594833cb656107","tid"